<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Students who receive a rating of 3 to 5 on the Advanced Placement Examinations will be considered for college credit and/or advanced placement.  Policies vary with the student's desire to use the credits in a major or in an elective area.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.benedictine.edu/coursecatalog" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

